I should not complain about free stuff, but honestly, how do YIFY torrents classify as '720p BRRip'? While i understand that for the equivalent size of a DVDrip, these do indeed have better quality than a standard DVDrip, and i praise YIFY for that. But seriously, when compared to a proper 720p, this is absolutely BULLSHIT! Maybe you should name your torrents 'Slightly better than a DVDRip' instead of '720p BRRip'. And before someone says, "Don't download it if you don't like it.", i actually get other people to download stuff for me cause i don't have a good internet connection, and i tell them to download only 720p BRRips, and most of them end up downloading this shit, and why, because this is LISTED AS A 720p BRRIP and due to its size, everyone is like "oo this can save some space on my hard disk, and it says 720p so it must be good!" and then they give me this shit.
